        },
        "text": "On consideration of the resolution Agreed to by the Yeas and Nays: 212 - 211 (Roll no. 186).",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H36600",
        "actionDate": "2025-07-02",
        "actionTime": "09:18:30",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Mr. McGovern moved On consideration of the resolution.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H8D000",
        "actionDate": "2025-07-02",
        "actionTime": "09:05:33",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "POINT OF ORDER - Mr. McGovern raised a point of order against the provisions of H. Res. 566 on the grounds that the resolution violates section 426(a) of the Congressional Budget Act. The Chair announced that the disposition of the point of order would be resolved by the question of consideration of H. Res. 566. The House proceeded with 20 minutes of debate on the point of order at the end of which the Chair will put the question on consideration.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H30000",
        "actionDate": "2025-07-02",
        "actionTime": "09:04:17",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Considered as privileged matter. (consideration: CR H3039-3059; text: CR H3040)",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H8D000",
        "actionDate": "2025-07-02",
        "actionTime": "09:04:12",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "By direction of the Committee on Rules, Ms. Foxx called up H.Res. 566 and asked for its immediate consideration.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H12420",
        "actionDate": "2025-07-02",
        "calendarNumber": {
          "calendar": "H00035"
        },
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Placed on the House Calendar, Calendar No. 35.",
        "type": "Calendars"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H12700",
        "actionDate": "2025-07-02",
        "actionTime": "09:00:02",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "The resolution makes in order a motion that the House concur in the Senate amendment to H.R. 1 and provides for one hour of debate.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H12100",
